[20/08/2017 03:56:19] <font color="#00ff00">Fijaos, qué caballita,</font>
[20/08/2017 03:56:19] <font color="#00ff00">esta es perfecta.</font>
[20/08/2017 03:56:21] <font color="#00ff00">Esta caballa es perfecta.</font>
