[20/08/2017 23:44:09] <font color="#00ff00">Españoles de mierda.</font>
[20/08/2017 23:44:17] <font color="#0000ff">(Gruñidos)</font>
[20/08/2017 23:44:38] <font color="#0000ff">(Rugidos)</font>
[20/08/2017 23:44:46] <font color="#ffffff">Podía ser peor.</font>
